<p align=justify> 
Some of the data of the new release were already present in the previous release, for example the
'Ca1_SR' file with some of Ca I lines or the 'nd2_exp' file with experimental data from Wisconsin group. 
These data are included in the new files 'Ca_recommend' and 'wisc_vald2_new', the old files 'Ca1_SR' 
and 'nd2_exp' are removed from the configuration file.
<p>

<br> Best Regards
<br> The VALD team

